nd buffer management\n\n5. **Supporting Components**:\n   - Selectable.java: Interface defining the contract for socket-aware selectable objects\n   - Receive.java: Interface for receiving network data\n   - Send.java: Interface for sending network data\n   - TransportLayer.java: Abstraction for transport-level I/O operations\n   - ChannelBuilder.java: Factory interface for creating configured channels\n   - RequestChannelMetrics.java: Metrics collection for the RequestChannel\n\nThe flow proceeds as: Client connections → Acceptor threads (per listener) → Processor threads (with Selector) → RequestChannel → Handler threads → Response back through Processor threads → Selector → NetworkSend → Socket.\n"
}

